                    <h3>Buyers research before they buy.</h3>
                    <p>Before anyone calls you, they look you up. Your website, your case studies, your continuing education record, your social presence. We make sure what they find earns the meeting.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-card-number">03 / SALES READY</div>
                    <h3>Warm leads close better.</h3>
