            <h2>What people ask before they call.</h2>

            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What does SkyKPI actually do?</h3>
                    <p>Two things. We run marketing for precast producers, the suppliers and service providers behind them, and AEC companies. We run operations for industry associations. Both services are built on the same idea, which is that the AEC industry needs people who already know it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Do you only work with precast producers?</h3>
                    <p>No. Many of our clients are the companies that supply precast producers with materials, equipment, services, and technology. The buyer is the same. The market is the same. The depth we bring works for both sides of the relationship.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Why pick a precast specialist over a bigger agency?</h3>
                    <p>A bigger agency has to learn your industry on your retainer. We already know how precast plants work, how specs get written, who makes the product call, and how a job gets won at the design phase before it ever shows up on a bid list. That speed is worth real money.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What is association management and why would we need it?</h3>
                    <p>Most associations were built around one full time executive director. That model is breaking under the weight of bigger memberships, more complex events, and constant communication expectations. We provide a full team for one monthly fee. Operations, membership, events, marketing, and communications, all under one roof.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Do you work outside AEC?</h3>
                    <p>No. We do not. The specialty is the value.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Where are you located?</h3>
                    <p>Frankfort, Illinois, about thirty minutes south of Chicago. We work with clients nationwide and travel as the work requires.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
